CREATE VIEW univmed.dim_audit_end
AS
SELECT
    [CRM_UNIV]
,[MEDICO_UNIV]
,[ESPECIALIDADE_UNIV]
,[LOGRADOURO_UNIV]
,[BAIRRO_UNIV]
,[CIDADE_UNIV]
,[CEP_UNIV]
,[ORIGEM_UNIV]
,[UF_UNIV]
,[BRICK_UNIV]
,[TELEFONE_UNIV]
,[KEY_CRM_UNIV]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_audit_end.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
 [CRM_UNIV]      VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MEDICO_UNIV]			VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ESPECIALIDADE_UNIV]	VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[LOGRADOURO_UNIV]		VARCHAR(100) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[BAIRRO_UNIV]			VARCHAR(100) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CIDADE_UNIV]			VARCHAR(100) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CEP_UNIV]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ORIGEM_UNIV]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[UF_UNIV]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[BRICK_UNIV]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TELEFONE_UNIV]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_CRM_UNIV]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) AS ROW
